data.description: Welcome home to endless opportunities with this 3-4 bedroom home with 1 full bathroom.  Spacious kitchen with ample cupboards and a main floor laundry.  Separate dining room and space for a home office or expanded living area. Newer roof, electrical, plumbing and hot water heater.  Don't forgot the attached 2 car garage and mud room.  Beautifully landscaped yard all close to schools, parks and shopping.  Call today for your personal showing!
